70
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:17,620
I mean, you start out with good intentions

71
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,741
and people end up working overtime,

72
00:03:19,761 --> 00:03:20,781
which fucks their lives.

73
00:03:23,021 --> 00:03:23,442
I mean,

74
00:03:26,122 --> 00:03:29,403
being one of the 30 odd percent of Kickstarter games

75
