1357
01:00:29,540 --> 01:00:31,361
because everybody has problems and everybody,

1358
01:00:31,501 --> 01:00:32,181
if they don't have problems,

1359
01:00:32,201 --> 01:00:33,401
they'll invent them and they want to talk about them.

